    span.italic So there you go. I hope you found this useful. Massive thank you to!{' '}
      a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maguireannie/" target="_blank") Annie
      | . She did all the hard work.
  p
    span.italic If you'd like to work with an awesome copywriter, do!{' '}
      a(href="https://anniemaguire.com/#contact" target="_blank") get in touch
      |!{' '}with her.